I Will call you Dear, becauſe I like you. A Gentleman and I have been reading your Dialogue between YOU and YOURSELF, and he admires your SOUL, but I could not help repeating with your Name-ſake in the Play,



                                 I take the BODY, you the MIND;


                                 Which has the better Bargain?

